Name: Dark Alley Elf
About the game: Dark Alley Elf is an action-platformer featuring hot and heavy sexual content. Take your trusty iron pipe and fight your way through several unique enemies, going from street to street until you reign the back alleys as slut supreme. In a modern-era world where fantasy races coexist peacefully alongside humans- Francesca the dark elf has found herself embroiled in a high stakes competition with her long time rival, famed company heiress Annabelle. The challenge? Be the one to earn the most money in a week's time. Stacked against almost impossible odds, Francesca decides to do what she does best- practicing the world's oldest profession on the seedy big city streets. Dark Alley Elf features a diverse grab bag of content and gameplay systems: NAVIGATE through the dangerous city streets and sewers! SMASH your way past an onslaught of lecherous thugs! COLLECT power-ups which aid you in your quest! LUST over a variety of hot interactive sex scenes! JAM OUT to a fully original soundtrack full of jazzy goodness!
